Package: boat-container-store
Architecture: all
Tag: role::container-store
Description: Boat container application store for Cockpit Container Apps
 This package provides the store definition and branding for the Boat
 container application store, designed to work with cockpit-container-apps
 on a HALPI2 running HaLOS.
 .
 When installed alongside cockpit-container-apps, it enables a curated view
 of boat-specific applications: Home Assistant for automation, Music
 Assistant for streaming and local-library playback, and a Snapcast client
 for HDMI audio output.
 .
 The store filters packages with the `field::boat` debtag.
